        "subject": "LU-9943 lnet: fix queue size in ENOMEM case.",
        "message": "LU-9943 lnet: fix queue size in ENOMEM case.\n\nChanging a WR count without queue size change caused\na IB error\n  mlx5_ib_post_send:4184:(pid 26272): Failed to prepare WQE\ndue situation when o2iblnd code allocate a more tx's when\nQP settings.\nLets adjust a connection queue depth to reflect a WR\nqueue size changes.\n\nFixes a 4083806828a94ee09c2dadf2cca8c224547d5ebc\n\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-4572\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey.lyashkov@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I4146d36c3b1830918dbf677254910d70b2ff6aab\n"
